      <div id="mmi-43584" class="scrolling-text-module colspan-4 rag measurable magic-module" data-event-category="magic_module/scrolling_text_module/43584" data-event-label="Scrolling Text Module 43584 (11/77)" data-instance-id="43584" data-id="107169">                  <div class="scrolling-text-module__inner" style="max-height: 240.0em" tabindex="0">
    
    <span style="font-size:18px"><strong>Students needed for video—and free headshots!</strong></span><br>
<br>
On Thursday, April 10, the Office of Development will be filming at locations around campus. You can sign up for a 10-minute slot to appear in front of the camera for a video portrait. We’ll send you your headshot afterwards, and you may be selected to appear among a montage of “humans of Yale” in our thank-you video to donors. <a href="https://calendly.com/2025-yale-video" target="_blank">Sign up here!</a>
</div>

