    <span style="font-size:18px"><strong>Yale Planetary Solutions Invites Proposals for the 4th Annual Grant Program</strong></span><br>
<br>
YPS is excited to announce a revised grant program for 2025, seeking to catalyze work on planetary challenges from across the university. More than $2M is available to support faculty and staff projects that create new knowledge, spark action, and drive impact.<br>
<br>
YPS is seeking proposals that align with our mission, and particularly with one or more of our primary lenses: climate change; biodiversity and ecosystems; and communities and society. This year, YPS will award three grant types, with support ranging from $25,000 to $250,000, in response to growing and diversifying demand.<br>
<br>
<strong>Deadline: March 30, 2025.</strong> <a href="https://planetarysolutions.yale.edu/yale-planetary-solutions-invites-proposals-4th-annual-grant-program" target="_blank">Full information &amp; apply &gt;</a>
