    <span style="font-size:18px"><strong>Participate in Yale @ Climate Week NYC 2025!</strong></span><br>
<br>
Yale Planetary Solutions invites expressions of interest from faculty, staff and students who have an event idea they would like considered for Yale @ Climate Week NYC. Our broad frame for this year’s events is transforming visions of hopeful futures into reality through impactful, practical planetary solutions.  We anticipate events will take place Tuesday, September 23 through Thursday, September 25.  Events selected will receive space and logistical support, event organizers will be responsible for coordinating their speaker details as appropriate. Please submit your idea by April 14.  Decisions will be communicated no later than April 25.  Please direct any questions to <a href="mailto:planetarysolutions@yale.edu" target="_blank"></a><a href="mailto:planetarysolutions@yale.edu">planetarysolutions@yale.edu</a>. <br>
