      <div id="mmi-43683" class="scrolling-text-module colspan-4 rag measurable magic-module" data-event-category="magic_module/scrolling_text_module/43683" data-event-label="Scrolling Text Module 43683 (46/77)" data-instance-id="43683" data-id="107302">                  <div class="scrolling-text-module__inner" style="max-height: 240.0em" tabindex="0">
    
    <span style="font-size:18px"><strong>Entrepreneur seeks graphic identity for a protein shake bottle</strong></span><br>
<br>
“That will include the font, drawing out the animal in a certain style (examples will be provided), and designing the flavor of the shake. When we choose an individual for the project, I will share a word document containing the examples that we have made to showcase what exactly we are looking for in the project. In regards to the deadline of when the project is requested, It would be ideal to have the finished project done in two weeks. However, I do know that managing academics and a side project is difficult, and I will gratefully extend that deadline if need be. With payment, I will pay two hundred dollars and that will be open to negotiation. <br>
<br>
In regards to me choosing an individual to do this project, I would like to do a tiny interview process. This process could be done by having them email me copies of previous work, to ensure that the art style we are looking for matches theirs.”<br>
<br>
<a href="mailto:cronaund2004@gmail.com" target="_blank">Reach out to Nicholas Donaldo Cronauer if you’re interested in this project!</a>
