The Olympic Museum and the 3-2-1 Qatar Olympic and Sports Museum are thrilled to announce the first edition of the Olympic Heritage | Artists in Residence 2025, an extraordinary opportunity for artists working with digital and immersive media to critically engage with the world of sports culture and the Olympic legacy We would love for you to be a part of this transformative experience and contribute to the global conversation on sports culture and the Olympic history. <br>
